title: Cay Thi Queentrees Food USA Recalls Poultry Products Produced Without Benefit of Import Inspection
summary: WASHINGTON, Nov. 4, 2019 Cay Thi Queentrees Food USA, the importer of record, a Garden Grove, Calif. firm, is recalling approximately 43,848 pounds of poultry products that were imported and distributed in the United States without the benefit of FSIS import re-inspection, the U.S. Department...
